This is a standalone test script (not a pytest test) that:
- Uses hardcoded invalid file paths: "test_data_files/..." and "test_dictionaries/..."
- Is designed to be run directly as a script, not via pytest
- Requires specific test data files that are not part of the standard test fixtures

To re-enable:
